@startuml
actor "QA" as QA
participant "kiwi-mvc\nSistema principal" as MVC
participant "Agent_ApiKiwi\nHandoff API" as HANDOFF
participant "Orquestador\nkiwi_orchestrator" as ORQ
participant "Tool\nget_kiwimvc_session_docs" as DBTOOL
database "MongoDB kiwi-mvc\nDocumentations" as MONGO
participant "Agente A\nextract_uc_rf_agent" as A
participant "Agente B\nkiwi_gherkin_agent" as B
database "kiwi_drafts.json\nDraft store" as STORE
participant "Agente C\nreview_publish_agent" as C
participant "Kiwi TCMS" as KIWI

title Flujo real de agentes - Input/Output

== Entrada desde kiwi-mvc ==

QA -> MVC : Selecciona sesion y documentacion\nelige flujo automatico
MVC -> HANDOFF : POST /api/kiwi-mvc/handoff\nsource_session_id,\nproject_name,\nsession_name,\nrun_immediately=true

HANDOFF -> HANDOFF : Crear sesion ADK\ncon project_name,\nsource_session_id,\nsession_name

HANDOFF --> MVC : ok,\nagent_session_id,\nagent_user_id,\nagent_app_name,\nhandoff_url

HANDOFF -> ORQ : Prompt automatico:\nrecuperar documentacion y ejecutar flujo completo

== Recuperacion de documentacion ==

ORQ -> DBTOOL : get_kiwimvc_session_docs(source_session_id)
DBTOOL -> MONGO : Buscar documentacion de la sesion
MONGO --> DBTOOL : Documentos funcionales\nDRF/DDS + metadatos
DBTOOL --> ORQ : merged_content,\nproject_name,\nsource_session_id,\nsource_documents

== Agente A - Extraccion UC/RF ==

ORQ -> A : Input:\nmerged_content,\nproject_name,\nsource_session_id,\nsource_documents

A --> ORQ : Output JSON:\nproject_name,\nsource_session_id,\nsource_documents,\ndrf,\nuse_cases[],\nfunctional_requirements[],\nnotes[]

note right of A
El Agente A NO guarda datos.
Solo extrae UC y RF y devuelve JSON.
end note

== Agente B - Generacion y persistencia ==

ORQ -> B : Input:\nJSON del Agente A

B -> STORE : register_documentation_reference(...)
B -> STORE : save_use_case(...)
B -> STORE : save_functional_requirement(...)

loop Por cada caso de uso
  B -> B : Generar escenarios Gherkin\n@direct y @derived
  B -> STORE : save_draft(summary,\ncategory_name,\ngherkin_text,\nmeta,\nproject_name,\nsource_session_id)
end

B --> ORQ : Markdown:\nAgente 1 - UC y RF\nAgente 2 - Gherkin por UC\nRevision - Pendiente de aprobacion

ORQ --> QA : Muestra borradores generados\npendientes de revision

note right of B
El Agente B NO publica en Kiwi.
Solo genera Gherkin y guarda borradores pendientes.
end note

== Revision de borradores ==

QA -> C : listar borradores
C -> STORE : list_drafts(status="pending", project_name)
STORE --> C : drafts[]
C --> QA : Lista de borradores

QA -> C : ver <summary>
C -> STORE : get_draft(summary, project_name)
STORE --> C : draft
C --> QA : Gherkin del borrador

alt QA anade feedback
  QA -> C : feedback <summary>: <texto>
  C -> STORE : add_feedback(summary, feedback)
  C -> STORE : get_draft(summary)
  STORE --> C : draft actual
  C -> C : Regenerar Gherkin aplicando feedback
  C -> STORE : save_draft(... nueva version ...)
  C --> QA : Borrador actualizado\npendiente de aprobacion

else QA rechaza borrador
  QA -> C : rechazar <summary>
  C -> STORE : delete_draft(summary, project_name)
  C --> QA : Borrador eliminado/rechazado

else QA acepta borrador
  QA -> C : aceptar <summary>
  C -> STORE : publish_draft(summary, project_name)
  STORE -> KIWI : TestCase.create(...)
  KIWI --> STORE : id caso creado / error
  STORE --> C : Resultado real de publicacion
  C --> QA : Caso publicado en Kiwi TCMS\ncon id o error
end

note right of C
El Agente C solo publica cuando QA dice
explicitamente "aceptar <summary>".
end note



@enduml